Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:35.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆无理的反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候多时了 baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间 如火一般与恶魔相会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来了吧 拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为购屋所存头款的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可在一段时间内边玩边吃牛肉饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人们并不知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被快乐所覆盖之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔便潜伏在背后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快将约好的东西交来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗？\N你那宝贝达令的偷腥行为照片及底片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:02:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该知道吧 baby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后过剩的欲望 对邀宴了邪恶的灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这卑鄙小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是梅雨季节的话 居然是个大太阳的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向恶行犯罪走之人的下场是悲惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但新的不幸正重重地压在留下来的人的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么做了这么恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下干脆我也沉沦算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 我的演技如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆从任何角度拍都能成画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我摄影师而言轻松许多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英格丽褒曼 洛琳白考儿\N都比不上拉姆的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 今天的午餐还是老样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别优待 加个小菜好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 我这摄影师兼现场导播有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷发 没事吧 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资金已经到谷底了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 吃了这餐后 几乎可说是没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影还真花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有心情感动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天就拍这几个cut
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处吃牛肉饭什么的\N并到处玩才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下只有中止制作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这次是全班募金开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果中止制作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌迟是逃不掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人兼导演会被冠以重大的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么用已拍摄的部分编辑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能就不用那么辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从开拍至今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只拍了五百尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你连剧本都未完成不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解制作电影的可怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 这样下去非常不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿有个有钱的支助者就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资金援助？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为何 我要为你的电影出钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不出吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得这是一桩好买卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此彻底地拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得会成为一部好电影的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后男主角 面堂终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听听你的片名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 对所有电影 片名只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“爱”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 多少资助点也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 您要出资 真是谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天放学后 体育馆见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底这是什么电影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这是你要将沉沦的拉姆说服的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆沉沦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我因细小之事沉沦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 然后拉姆改邪归正 对爱觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人便结合了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景3 cut-8
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,action
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊 你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你真正的面目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应是个具有善心美丽的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那衣服脱去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起到有歌声的饮料店\N过正正当当的青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗把脸 重头来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不顺从自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cut
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 你真是个了不起的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演技不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我有点劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下来个全体演员演出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助演出？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不是阿忍是不行的 请帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 只是普通女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因点小事误入歧途的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人只是在利用你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我所选择的路 和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深沉的爱 你难道不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我 我要和此人一起渡过一生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要走不良少年之路 我也将追随你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可没这段对白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 面堂不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cut cut
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 戏错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵 不要烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对达令做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 你这不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就这样 真实感 真实感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影这东西只看那么一下 就是不良少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果演电影的话 不就会被警察捉走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说些莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想在人生的路途上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法抬头挺胸的走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以变得像女孩点的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 可以变得像女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以变得像女孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要想想你父亲为何禁看电影便能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 想干吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要的比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 你那可爱的脸会留下疤的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是孩子 我叫阿丈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将你们干掉 我就能成为女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么理论？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想那么多琐碎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为电影的完成 任何手段必须正当化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就照那速度冲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 站起来 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cut
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很好 很有魄力小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要阻碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全上了火气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够真实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可以完成杰作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作电影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就犹如在未知世界中旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起先充满未知和期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到中途会担心是否能达到目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熬到拍摄完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星当第一次导演作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「爱即是一切」的特别试映会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 您在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影啊 电影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还真没规矩 放什么秘密电影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 让点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师不要挤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 请不要偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是早说过会在生活指导室放映的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因一点锁事沉沦\N拉姆 所投身之不良少年的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿他所看到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他们已化为行走中的火药库
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在发中藏凶器之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长裙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里面正是凶器的宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫把 炒菜匙一定具备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短枪及反战车飞弹也可配备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后变形学生服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如这没什么的太阳眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在电子科技的进步下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使其内部搭载雷射发射器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能在不久的未来出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多数的情况 他们渴望着爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那表现无法被扭曲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只能以被扭曲的方式表现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以半调子的爱情表现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会招到反击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爱情沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生们自主的自制电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师你还以为是什么电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是片名是校园暴力 好像不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 学生们会投入这个主题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示我们学校是和平的 也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还是个角度拍错的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 青春到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 青春和借出的钱是回不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清纯地 正直地 美丽地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家脱去旧外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那山上跑去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 举起我们青春的旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我就犹如白痴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也没变得像女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直拍摄的我居然没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我对高达 罗塞里尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 对艾森斯坦说什么才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么 阿忍 住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何 做了试演会算是对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点在我拍片历史中画上了污点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 上映中止了 知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又产生了一部幻影的电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原版软片 由我亲手烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易作的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会弄成如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作费有班上的募金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果上映中止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不还钱的话是不会罢休的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽这么说用掉的钱也回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么努力作的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才说中止 没这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是募了金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看的权力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么给我们看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想让你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有底片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就上映嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想上映 而且猛烈地想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答得完全没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为面堂不让我上映嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那片子只是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对嘛 一点也未拍出人性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍出人性是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拍科幻超级学园暴力\N大场面爱情闹剧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 这是什么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事我从未听过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的话就不会演出了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很适合作喜剧演员 却在那装优等生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼的家伙 什么叫喜剧演员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么样看也是稳重派的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们被拍摄没发觉有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也未发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真呆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多多少少发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没想到会到此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是放映机已坏了 想看也无法看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 放映机带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对上映 反对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好压制好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 片架装不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么现在才说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 改良一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会爆炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插座 插座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这个规格不对啊 进不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下 我来改造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 我再说一次 不要制造爆炸事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会爆炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 还真疑心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二年四班教室的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是什么装扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有挑战的人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个暴学院的人 来挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌巴巴那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一个 那一个 全是一幅软弱的脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这学校没有人有胆子敢瞪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁放雁子飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点回家可会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果败给少爷 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这背后的指标在晚间会痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子加速装置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃啊 这学校的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是生化人或机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校的学生还满行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师虽在角落但都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何的坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱着学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 夕阳真美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结得好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我导的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:22:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到放映中的人物会跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我的机器规格还是不符
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家 脱去旧有的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那山上一起奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 举起我们青春的旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将诸星家卷入狂澜的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在女家司及御入道的影子中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着樱花及Cherry二十年的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:23:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为何会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想为达令做好吃的料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大决战 樱花对错乱坊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
